channeldata.description: This repository contains add-on widgets and classes for applications that use the Qt Widgets module. If you are porting applications from KDE Platform 4 "kdeui" library, you will find many of its classes here.  Provided are action classes that can be added to toolbars or menus, a wide range of widgets for selecting characters, fonts, colors, actions, dates and times, or MIME types, as well as platform-aware dialogs for configuration pages, message boxes, and password requests.
